Second Department,

December, 1955

(December 5, 1955) Carmine A. Cavallaro, Respondent, v. Martin Stettin et al., Doing Business as Stettin Brothers, Appellants.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Appellate Division denied, without costs. Present — Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Beldoek, Murphy and Ughetta, JJ.
